# Use AGENTS.md for project guidance

This project follows the [AGENTS.md](https://agents.md) standard for guiding AI coding agents.

- **Read AGENTS.md** at the repository root for project context, layout, workflows, conventions, and key files.
- **Treat AGENTS.md as the primary source** of project-specific instructions—equivalent to or in place of CLAUDE.md.
- When working in this repo, consult AGENTS.md first for setup, code style, testing, PR instructions, and repository structure.
- AGENTS.md is stewarded by the Agentic AI Foundation under the Linux Foundation; use it as the single, predictable place for agent instructions.
